TITLE: Orchestrator and Runtime Pipeline Capability
STATEMENT: >>>
GHOST shall provide a runtime orchestration spine that coordinates the active SuperPrompt, legal pipeline stage order, implemented stage calls, current GUI runner behavior, and final prompt/send-boundary direction without duplicating the internal ownership of preprocessing, knowledge, memory, agent, UI, logging, or runtime-platform subsystems.
<<<

