<<<

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SRS-FR-ORCH-003
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: SuperPrompt Runtime Truth
STATEMENT: >>>
The active SuperPrompt shall be treated as the session runtime truth for pipeline state, stage/history fields, retrieval state, memory context state, and prompt-ready rendering state.
<<<

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SRS-FR-ORCH-004
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Final Prompt and Send Boundary
